The paper deals with navigation in unknown environments, which is a common problem in robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks for learning perception-action loops, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the use of sensory input, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper discusses the use of memory units in neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
